summary: Ayaan Gazali is a Research Assistant at UROP, San Jose State University, with expertise in software development, AI applications, and fintech, actively seeking software engineering and fintech internships. With extensive experience as a Teaching Assistant at Stanford and an Investment Banking Intern at Kamco Invest, Ayaan is keen on roles at the intersection of AI, systems, and finance.
